strings.Value: "I swear, Regongar, if it weren't for our common cause, I'd challenge you to a duel and wipe that smug sneer off your face!"

"Why, Your Nobleness, you mustn't challenge the peasantry to duels! How unseemly it would be if they spanked you! No, you rather must spank them! Spank them with a whip! I'm taking off my pants right now!"
